  "extrastuck.ponder.cruxtruder.header": "Getting Cruxite Dowels out of your Cruxtruder",
  "extrastuck.ponder.cruxtruder.text_1": "This is the Cruxtruder, which is the source of cruxite dowels",
  "extrastuck.ponder.cruxtruder.text_2": "Start by removing that pesky Lid",
  "extrastuck.ponder.cruxtruder.text_3": "(You may need to feed raw cruxite to the pipe)",
  "extrastuck.ponder.cruxtruder.text_4": "Turn the wheel in front of the pipe...",
