  "extrastuck.ponder.cruxtruder.text_6": "Just click (or punch) the dowel to drop it",
  "extrastuck.ponder.holopad.header": "Decorating your home with a Holopad",
  "extrastuck.ponder.holopad.text_1": "The Holopad allows displaying what is in a punched card",
  "extrastuck.ponder.holopad.text_2": "Just place a punched card, and enjoy!",
  "extrastuck.ponder.intellibeam.header": "Reading the unreadable with the Intellibeam Laserstation",
  "extrastuck.ponder.intellibeam.text_1": "Some items' captcha codes are too complex to be read normally",
  "extrastuck.ponder.intellibeam.text_2": "The Intellibeam Laserstation can decipher these codes",
  "extrastuck.ponder.intellibeam.text_3": "Just put the card in...",
  "extrastuck.ponder.intellibeam.text_4": "...click it a few times...",
  "extrastuck.ponder.intellibeam.text_5": "...and the card's captcha code is finally readable",
  "extrastuck.ponder.or_alchemy.header": "Combining items with the Punch Designix",
  "extrastuck.ponder.or_alchemy.text_1": "It is possible to create new items using the Punch Designix",
